item.dc:creator: @LilXCj LilXCj
item.description:
@LilXCj wrote:

item.cfg

search for

initiate

The first few numbers depend on what your item.java says

ex.

item = 14484 dragon claws TAB(a lot) a TAB b TAB c

a = low alch return value
b = high alch return value
c = shop price buy & sell value
